reviewText:
If the first episode is a meditation on power, this one is a meditation on control. Godkiller delivers again with a punch. A bit more philosophical (early Henri Bergson) than the first, and it will leave you wanting to see how this psychological landscape evolves in the 3rd episode.

You'll want to pick this one up quickly, sure to be a legendary series from the famed director Matt Pizzolo. Walk Among Them! Walk Among Us NOW!
